{"tid":2040061,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"聯署呼籲美國總統中止香港獨立關稅區地位","createTime":"2020-05-28T10:42:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-30T04:11:23.000Z","uid":50306,"like":12,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c9c2e2766d1ef947d9f2c853985558b40b6bf60c","tid":2040061,"uid":50306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T10:42:00.000Z","msg":"唔講咁多喇，簽左先<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TEXAR22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTEXAR22.jpg&h=9cc4d21a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【香港人要求中止獨立關稅區地位之聯署】<br />\n<br />\n面對中共強行通過港版《國家安全法》，明顯違反《中英聯合聲明》和《基本法》，美國國務卿蓬佩奧已直宣香港高度自治不再。多個香港人團體現發起聯署，呼籲美國總統中止香港獨立關稅區地位。<br />\n<br />\n香港過往作為中國主要離岸金融中心，大量外資直接投資及離岸銀行貸款經香港進入中國金融體系。要對抗中共經濟干預，最有力武器就是中止香港的特殊地位。<br />\n<br />\n本次聯署目標為2020年6月7日前達到200萬香港人聯署，極需不同團體、市民自發擺放街站收集簽名；亦歡迎廣傳各地支持香港的朋友參與，海外聯署數字將分開列出。聯署信將會遞交予美國駐港領事送呈美國白宮，同時向全球媒體發佈聯署數字。<br />\n<br />\n聯署網址：<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/SecureHKFreedomFormNew\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FSecureHKFreedomFormNew&d=hmvw4%2FD%2BM9RG0cIfJpNLu7P2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=0c9509e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/SecureHKFreedomFormNew</a><br />\n<br />\n聯署團體名單 (不斷更新)︰<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/OrganizationsSignatories\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FOrganizationsSignatories&d=hmvw4%2FD%2BM9RG0cIfJpNLu7P2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=789949c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/OrganizationsSignatories</a><br />\n<br />\n實體聯署表格：<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/SecureHKFreedomPFormNew\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FSecureHKFreedomPFormNew&d=hmvw4%2FD%2BM9RG0cIfJpNLu7P2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=7e2ce2cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/SecureHKFreedomPFormNew</a><br />\n<br />\n實體簽名表請於6月7日前電郵至 petition@SecureHKFreedom.org ，以便計入聯署總數。"},{"pid":"4cd628f8e532e594c4d50d32cbf06fb31ff21baf","tid":2040061,"uid":328890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T10:42:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4bcf8d9bc57be4675c9c7c667438a1f5573a3667","tid":2040061,"uid":50306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T10:48:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e6a6080b80cd587be0cbaeb4ba6a73b5ef22eefe","tid":2040061,"uid":50306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T10:48:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"da8db117cadd02ef28b935605f7eb17a6788fa3e","tid":2040061,"uid":50306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T10:48:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9895d8aa98911828476979fabfb3ade8598d0045","tid":2040061,"uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T10:48:45.000Z","msg":"白宮聯署: 港版國安法一成立, 取消香港關係法, 獨立關稅區, 敏感科技不准入香港<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-abolishment-us-hk-policy-act-once-hk-security-law-established\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frequest-abolishment-us-hk-policy-act-once-hk-security-law-established&d=hmvw4%2FD%2BM9RG0cIfJpNLu7P2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=c8ef5e5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-abolishment-us-hk-policy-act-once-hk-security-law-established</a>"},{"pid":"b24311443b3bb059bee9d72089f208ef9edda6ec","tid":2040061,"uid":32220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T10:49:19.000Z","msg":"美國今晚就出黎宣布停關稅地位啦，點會唔做野"},{"pid":"9aa68d1244d0f6fdd67f429ff391ef70cf18e3f2","tid":2040061,"uid":132854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T10:49:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2ef26e656be9ff7ca5fee04bcf49c5ab82a4da7b","tid":2040061,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T10:49:36.000Z","msg":"On9?<br />\n就係要佢制裁wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b379cbccb439cf10ee7a94b58004